    "Our task is to detect whether the generated answer suffers from hallucinations.",
    "The few-shot prompt is constructed as a sequence of query-answer pairs.",
    "The pairs are denoted by {(q i, a i)} n i=1, where q i represents a query and a i its corresponding answer.",
    "The prompt can be expressed as follows:",
    "The F LLM is queried with the concatenation of the query Q on top of the prompt P f orward, which retrieves a generated answer denoted by A *, signifying the response to the query Q."
